<section class="about section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img class="img-responsive" src="~/images/about/about.jpeg">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="mt-40">About Our Pharmacy</h2>
                <p>
                    Welcome to our pharmacy, where we are committed to providing top-quality healthcare services and products to our valued customers.
                    With years of experience, our team of dedicated pharmacists and healthcare professionals ensures that you receive the best care possible, whether you're managing a chronic condition, seeking advice on over-the-counter products, or filling prescriptions.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We strive to be more than just a pharmacy by offering personalized consultations, prescription management, and home delivery services, ensuring that your healthcare needs are met with convenience and care. We believe in building lasting relationships with our customers based on trust and reliability.
                </p>
                
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-40">
            <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
                <img src="~/images/about/awards-logo.png">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
                <img src="~/images/about/awards-logo.png">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
                <img src="~/images/about/awards-logo.png">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
                <img src="~/images/about/awards-logo.png">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
